OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDavid Walliams: 'Harmful'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FChinese character removed  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffrom children's book       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A David Walliams story about a Chinese 
OL,6, boy is to be removed from one of his   
OL,7, children's books after criticism that  
OL,8, it contained "harmful stereotypes".    
OL,10,FA new edition of The World's Worst     
OL,11,FChildren will be released next year    
OL,12,Fwithout the story Brian Wong, Who Was  
OL,13,FNever, Ever Wrong.                     
OL,15,FThe move comes after podcaster Georgie 
OL,16,FMa complained the book was "normalising
OL,17,Fjokes on minorities from a young age". 
OL,19,FAfter meeting Ma, its publishers       
OL,20,Fconfirmed the story would be replaced. 
